@required {resourceGroupName: any # The name of the resource group., tapName: any # The name of virtual network tap.}
@returns(200) Request successful. The operation returns the resulting VirtualNetworkTap resource.

@endpoint PUT /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworkTaps/{tapName}
@desc Creates or updates a Virtual Network Tap.
@required {resourceGroupName: any # The name of the resource group., tapName: any # The name of the virtual network tap., parameters: any # Parameters supplied to the create or update virtual network tap operation.}
@returns(200) Update successful. The operation returns the resulting VirtualNetworkTap resource.
@returns(201) Create successful. The operation returns the resulting VirtualNetworkTap resource.

@endpoint PATCH /subscriptions/{subscriptionId}/resourceGroups/{resourceGroupName}/providers/Microsoft.Network/virtualNetworkTaps/{tapName}
